data.description: Beautiful, cozy home in the heart of Angleton on 1/2 an acre with pecan trees and an oversized garage! Make this home your own, and enjoy the luxuries of living in the city while also having a spacious outdoor oasis to relax and wind down in...  With schools and many amenities nearby, you won't want to miss this great opportunity!
